OL,6,FA lecturer in Mathematics at the
OL,7,FUniversity of Bristol has been praised
OL,8,Fat an awards ceremony dubbed the
OL,9,F'Oscars of Science'.
OL,11,FDr Laura Monk won the 2024
OL,12,FBreakthrough Prizes at the awards
OL,13,Fceremony in the Academy Museum of
OL,14,FMotion Picture Arts and Sciences in
OL,15,FLos Angeles on Saturday 13 April.
