OL,3,CMaths lecturer presented with award by
OL,4,CVenus Williams in LA
OL,6,FTennis superstar Venus Williams and
OL,7,FAvatar actress Zoe Saldana presented
OL,8,FDr Monk with the Maryam Mirzakhani New
OL,9,FFrontiers Prize for her research in
OL,10,Fspectral geometry, an area of maths
OL,11,Fstudying the relationship between the
OL,12,Fvibrational modes of surfaces and
OL,13,Ftheir geometry.
OL,15,FDr Monk, who has an eight-month-old
OL,16,Fdaughter, said: "Winning this award
OL,17,Fwas one of the proudest moments of my
OL,18,Fwhole life, second to the birth of
OL,19,FLily.
