OL,3,CMaths lecturer presented with award by
OL,4,CVenus Williams in LA
OL,6,F"I'm also so grateful to my husband
OL,7,FAlexei, who is looking after our baby
OL,8,Fwhile I enjoy this amazing experience
OL,9,Fwhich is beyond my wildest dreams."
OL,11,FBill Gates, Elon Musk, Lizzo, and Katy
OL,12,FPerry also attended the ceremony.
OL,14,FDr Monk said: "The whole occasion was
OL,15,Fhugely impressive and I certainly
OL,16,Fdidn't expect to meet so many A-list
OL,17,Fcelebrities.
OL,19,F"It was quite a surreal experience
OL,20,Fwhen such famous people approach you
OL,21,Fand ask questions about what you do."
