OL,4,CVenus Williams in LA
OL,6,FThe award was created in honour of
OL,7,Fpioneering Iranian mathematician
OL,8,FMaryam Mirzakhani, who died of breast
OL,9,Fcancer aged 40 in 2017.
OL,11,FDr Monk said: "Maryam Mirzakhani has
OL,12,Fbeen a big inspiration for me and my
OL,13,FPhD was inspired by her amazing work.
OL,15,F"Sadly, we never had the chance to
OL,16,Fmeet but she exchanged emails with my
OL,17,Fadvisor Nalini Anantharaman asking
OL,18,Fquestions, which we have since
OL,19,Fanswered. That's such a special
OL,20,Ffeeling."
