OL,6,FThe Breakthrough Prize celebrates
OL,7,Fresearch achievements of the world's
OL,8,Ftop scientists. Dr Monk has gained
OL,9,Fjust over #40,000 for her award.
OL,11,FDr Monk said: "I was lost for words
OL,12,Fwhen I got the call saying I had won.
OL,13,FThe money is helping us to buy a house
OL,14,Fand we feel incredibly thankful."
